  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the role, the safety and the effectiveness of
      Intravitreal Bevacizumab injections as an adjunct to vitrectomy in the management of severe
      proliferative diabetic retinopathy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
